# =============================================================================
# WHAT IS INTENTIONALLY OPEN (documented here for clarity)
# =============================================================================
#
# The following are NOT ignored and are open to the world:
#
#   PHILOSOPHY.md              — Mission, ethics, design philosophy
#   README.md                  — Project overview
#   LICENSE.md                 — License with ethical use clause
#   docs/                      — Architecture decisions, API contracts
#   src/sanctum-ai/            — Core AI layer protocols
#   src/architecture/          — Type system and formal specifications
#   src/lib/                   — Shared utilities and governance logic
#   src/components/            — UI components
#   src/pages/                 — Application pages
#   src/hooks/                 — React hooks
#   src/contexts/              — React contexts
#   src/types/                 — TypeScript types
#   backend/src/sanctum/       — COS plane interfaces
#   backend/src/routes/        — API route definitions
#   supabase/migrations/       — Database schema (no data)
#   supabase/functions/        — Edge function source (no secrets)
#   chain/                     — Blockchain protocol definitions
#   plaas/                     — Platform-as-a-service layer definitions
#   database/migrations/       — SQL schema migrations
#   .env.example               — Environment variable documentation
#   openapi.yaml               — API specification
#   vite.config.ts             — Build configuration
#   tailwind.config.ts         — Design system config
#   tsconfig*.json             — TypeScript configuration
#
# CLOSED (gitignored):
#
#   .env / .env.*              — All secrets and credentials
#   *.tfstate / .terraform/    — Terraform state (real resource IDs)
#   terraform.tfvars           — Infrastructure variable values
#   *secret*.yaml              — Kubernetes secrets
#   backend/logs/              — Application logs (may contain PII)
#   screenshots/               — Dev snapshots
#   eslint-report.*            — Generated CI reports
#   earth2studio-project/      — Broken install artifacts
#   azure-*.json               — Azure deployment configs with endpoints
#   pentest/ / security-audit/ — Vulnerability details
#   indigenous-knowledge/sacred/ — Sovereign cultural data (FPIC)
#   research/internal/         — Unpublished research
#   contracts/ / agreements/   — Partner agreements
#
# =============================================================================
